{
  "name": "Icon",
  "summary": "<p><strong>Icon</strong> 对象是从 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconSet/IconSet .htm#IconSet.IconSet\">IconSet</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconSet/IconSet .htm#IconSet.Item\">Item</a></strong> 属性中返回的。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第一个图标集条件格式的图标集中所有图标的索引。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第二个图标集条件格式的图标集中第一个图标的实际类型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> icon = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(icon.<span class=\"hljs-property\">constructor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表用于条件格式规则的图标集中的单个图标。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Index",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，该值指明 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconSet/IconSet .htm#IconSet.IconSet\">IconSet</a></strong> 对象中 <strong>Icon</strong> 对象的索引号。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第一个图标集条件格式的图标集中第一个图标的索引。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> icon = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(icon.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第二个图标集条件格式的图标集中第二个图标的索引赋值给 D1 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> icon = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = icon.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
